Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.05,0:00:16.24,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This building was originally\Na 14th-century castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.24,0:00:20.20,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It was converted into a hotel\Nin the early 1900s.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.20,0:00:23.48,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But it closed 10 years ago\Nwhen its owner died.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.76,0:00:28.30,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now Kars has turned it into a shelter\Nfrom the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.89,0:00:30.97,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy lurks within.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.51,0:00:36.05,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But JoJo and Lisa Lisa\Nknow nothing of the hotel's layout.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.39,0:00:50.93,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,From the silent depths
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.43,0:00:58.05,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The pillars awaken from ages-long sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.14,0:01:05.39,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Crimson blood
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.05,0:01:12.14,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Summons the valorous to stand up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.85,0:01:20.43,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If inherited love is called fate
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.51,0:01:26.72,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then take another step with smiling eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.39,0:01:33.22,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mystify the darkness, dodge in a blink
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.26,0:01:36.97,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Avoid the blade,\Nfind an opening and strike
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.05,0:01:43.01,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Conviction tested\Nopens the way to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.26,0:01:47.72,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Like a bloody storm\NHot like a bloody stone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.80,0:01:51.60,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Destiny written into your veins
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.68,0:01:57.39,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The undying bonds of honor arise
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.43,0:02:03.05,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Take hold of them
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.56,0:02:12.05,Type,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chapter 21: A Hundred Against Two
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.56,0:02:09.56,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.94,0:02:12.40,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the creepy cobwebs?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.40,0:02:13.82,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Clean the place!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.40,0:02:18.57,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We're depressed enough\Nwithout these decorations!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.82,0:02:21.91,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But look at this trail of blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.53,0:02:26.12,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wamuu took a heavy beating from Hamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.75,0:02:31.08,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Caesar didn't go down without a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.55,0:02:39.93,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let Wamuu recover!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.55,0:02:43.26,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We're going in, Coach Lisa Lisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.56,0:02:47.47,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.47,0:02:48.64,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.23,0:02:52.81,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,T-This doorknob really grossed me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.02,0:02:56.23,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like\NI'm grabbing some guy's hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.98,0:02:58.32,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a door!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.32,0:02:59.15,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.24,0:03:04.37,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you looking for?\NI said I'm not a door.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.75,0:03:09.75,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A vampire!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.70,0:03:12.54,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Look out, JoJo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.21,0:03:17.96,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.34,0:03:25.05,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If it weren't for that weapon,\NI'd have peeled your face clean off!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.26,0:03:29.60,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Wired Beck.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.68,0:03:34.02,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I killed my lover,\Nbut escaped from prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.02,0:03:38.61,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But then Lord Kars made me\Npart of his gang with a mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.15,0:03:40.74,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He has my loyalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.90,0:03:46.49,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to let you go in\Nand disturb Lord Kars's rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.91,0:03:53.25,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Those fiends! So they're already\Nunleashing their hounds upon humans?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.63,0:03:57.00,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.21,0:04:00.76,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're just a pawn\Nthat's bound for hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.76,0:04:04.76,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Here, let me give you a little push\Ninto the abyss!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.30,0:04:07.05,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lisa Lisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.35,0:04:15.91,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Beautiful! Magnificent!\NSuch lovely skin you have!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.91,0:04:19.78,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hold me! Let me drink your life\Nthrough that skin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:22.43,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in a bad mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.75,0:04:27.31,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to hear from\Nor look at a worm like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.83,0:04:30.87,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But if you want to hold me, just try.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.62,0:04:34.33,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be the last thing you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.00,0:04:40.92,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Spikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.51,0:04:43.17,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.55,0:04:46.05,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They're spikes, not fingers!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.34,0:04:49.97,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's covered in wire-like body hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.26,0:04:54.16,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like it when women\Nmake jokes about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.64,0:04:58.36,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Girls who laugh at me get punished!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.11,0:05:03.16,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you a squeeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.40,0:05:05.71,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll hug you to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.71,0:05:08.16,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes! He's faster than I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.49,0:05:13.51,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Her scarf!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.51,0:05:17.33,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Her scarf\Nbecomes a Hamon-filled weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.92,0:05:20.38,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A scarf?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.34,0:05:24.09,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You want to catch me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.37,0:05:25.88,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.18,0:05:29.26,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And now I'm free!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.55,0:05:31.96,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Wha...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.95,0:05:33.46,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.46,0:05:35.39,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Come, JoJo. Let's move.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.60,0:05:37.01,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.60,0:05:41.98,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lisa Lisa's movements flow like silk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.27,0:05:44.65,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't waste any effort!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.94,0:05:47.23,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't ignore me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.78,0:05:48.78,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.78,0:05:52.79,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A woman like that\Nhas to be punished, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.79,0:05:55.69,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, friend. Your time is up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.69,0:05:58.18,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who got punished.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.18,0:06:00.46,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You got a dose of Hamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.38,0:06:03.67,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.77,0:06:18.85,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She's got what it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.85,0:06:24.44,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I thought she'd be weak in a fight,\Nbut she's better than me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.44,0:06:25.86,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.11,0:06:27.99,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She's my coach, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.57,0:06:30.86,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, JoJo...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.16,0:06:36.37,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,...you still haven't taken the antidote\NCaesar stole for you, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.58,0:06:39.37,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.83,0:06:40.71,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.38,0:06:43.96,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll drink it after I beat Wamuu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.38,0:06:49.88,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This ring isn't a promise between\NWamuu and me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.97,0:06:55.85,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's now a promise to Caesar\Nto fight and keep living.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.56,0:07:00.98,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lisa Lisa, will you hold it for me\Nuntil I need it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.52,0:07:03.48,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.11,0:07:06.36,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You should keep it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.40,0:07:09.67,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows what may happen to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.28,0:07:18.29,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,As they went deeper,\Nthe trail of blood grew ever thinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.54,0:07:23.96,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo and Lisa Lisa were fully aware\Nwhat that meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.29,0:07:27.46,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wamuu's wounds were healing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.16,0:07:32.09,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are they here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:45.61,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.61,0:07:49.86,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You've grown quite a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.28,0:07:53.74,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard, you killed Caesar!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.45,0:07:57.66,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, JoJo. Look at the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.99,0:08:01.37,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, my head is cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.87,0:08:05.29,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I noticed, too. The footprints, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.79,0:08:07.13,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There are two sets.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.50,0:08:11.05,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That means Kars is here! Where is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.63,0:08:13.97,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.43,0:08:19.10,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Two sets of footprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.47,0:08:22.51,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I feel dozens of lungs breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.98,0:08:26.96,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's her. I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.96,0:08:30.82,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're quite composed and\Nperceptive for a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.94,0:08:35.57,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can see how JoJo and Caesar\Nlearned so much so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.41,0:08:39.79,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And you can feel even slight breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.29,0:08:42.87,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're among the finest Hamon warriors.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.46,0:08:48.88,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wha-What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.26,0:08:52.42,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You, you're all vampires, aren't you?\NDamn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.38,0:08:57.86,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No response? That's creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.35,0:09:07.56,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kars!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.48,0:09:14.82,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Kars gave us, his chosen,\Neternal life!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.82,0:09:16.78,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's 100 against two!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.03,0:09:22.12,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When our master gives the order,\Nwe'll tear you both to shreds, JoJo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.51,0:09:37.43,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,T-This is bad. It's 100 on two.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.43,0:09:40.41,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lisa Lisa, we can't win this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.01,0:09:42.81,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Lord Kars.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.04,0:09:47.60,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Back in Rome, we promised\Nto fight each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.94,0:09:50.31,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I want revenge for Master Esidisi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.90,0:09:52.82,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please allow me to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.36,0:09:54.36,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I shall not.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.36,0:09:58.36,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Our goal is to obtain\Nthe Red Stone of Aja.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.11,0:10:00.62,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget that, Wamuu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.78,0:10:02.58,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.16,0:10:07.68,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. We can't.\NI'm not in the mood anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.68,0:10:10.04,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I know I could beat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.04,0:10:15.76,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But even if I did,\Nall these vampires are still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.01,0:10:19.48,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Win or lose, I'd still die, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.48,0:10:23.26,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With odds like that,\Ngiving up is only natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.51,0:10:25.98,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm throwing in the towel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.35,0:10:30.86,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Blast it! You all saw, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.19,0:10:35.11,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And I thought I could\Nzap them all at once, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.61,0:10:37.40,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now, kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.40,0:10:41.12,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you kill us,\Nyou'll never have the Stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.53,0:10:42.28,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hold!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.74,0:10:44.12,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's this, woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.33,0:10:48.91,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not stupid enough\Nto be carrying the Stone here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.16,0:10:53.88,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If one of us isn't\Nin a certain place at a certain time...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.46,0:10:57.30,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,...the Stone will be destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.01,0:11:04.51,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try to fool me, woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.01,0:11:09.06,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think\Nyou'll be able to find it in time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.35,0:11:14.52,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The bomb is a small thing,\Nbut is enough to damage the Stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.23,0:11:21.03,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is all this true? She never told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.03,0:11:23.32,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just run with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.49,0:11:25.75,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's all true!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.75,0:11:28.33,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If we die, boom! Kaboom!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.54,0:11:31.96,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, we can't let you\Nleave here alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.54,0:11:34.46,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have a suggestion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.26,0:11:38.51,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo and Wamuu can fight one-on-one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.82,0:11:42.47,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And Kars,\Nyou and I will fight one-on-one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.18,0:11:46.97,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And to the winner...goes the Stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.57,0:11:48.22,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.35,0:11:52.87,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The victor will win the Stone\Nand the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.27,0:11:54.86,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It will all be clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.52,0:11:58.83,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who will hold the stone, us or you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.36,0:12:03.45,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who will survive?\NThe Pillar Men or humankind?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.72,0:12:04.95,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.12,0:12:07.03,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wamuu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.08,0:12:10.00,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's laughable, Lord Kars.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.70,0:12:12.25,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,S-She's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.57,0:12:17.25,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She's a better gambler\Nthan I could even dream of being.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.17,0:12:20.63,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You've got pluck, woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.15,0:12:24.01,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. We fight for the Stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.48,0:12:25.84,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But don't get cocky!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.55,0:12:28.85,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You have no tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.34,0:12:34.60,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She just turned a dire situation\Ninto more-or-less even odds.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.82,0:12:37.87,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then. Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.70,0:12:55.58,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We need a proper time and place\Nfor our battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.29,0:12:58.46,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wamuu, your thoughts?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.92,0:13:03.17,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We fight tonight, under the full moon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.51,0:13:09.35,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The place will be at the foot of\NPiz Berlina, 15 km southeast of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.39,0:13:14.02,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We meet at the Skeleton's Heel\Nstone circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.48,0:13:19.40,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Many warriors found death\Nor glory in that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.15,0:13:21.48,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A stone circle?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.03,0:13:26.20,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you can't just pick a place\Nthat suits your fancy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.74,0:13:29.91,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wamuu, I think that's a fine choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.53,0:13:32.70,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now, about the Stone...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.04,0:13:33.70,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.20,0:13:39.50,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Bring the Stone to the Skeleton's Heel\Nat midnight tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.17,0:13:42.76,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And be sure to remove the bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.05,0:13:45.92,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The woman stays here as insurance!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.98,0:14:02.86,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lisa Lisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.11,0:14:05.57,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They don't want us to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.03,0:14:10.24,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's a reasonable request.\NGo and fetch the Stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.45,0:14:11.95,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.66,0:14:15.37,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Right. I'll see you at the arena.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.70,0:14:16.96,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.50,0:14:18.58,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.51,0:14:25.59,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Caesar...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.93,0:14:41.16,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Until yesterday,\NI lived only thinking of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.36,0:14:45.53,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But a new feeling burns inside me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.82,0:14:48.78,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is this compassion?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.91,0:14:54.38,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Curse it!\NI just want to wreck those bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.38,0:15:00.58,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll do it for Caesar, Meshina,\NLisa Lisa and the rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.38,0:15:03.09,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fight for you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.64,0:15:17.13,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, there's no bomb at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.13,0:15:21.19,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lisa Lisa, you're deceptive,\Neven under pressure!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.73,0:15:27.25,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now, maybe I should bring you\Na change of panties, hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.28,0:15:32.66,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What're these photos?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.34,0:15:35.37,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's Granny Erina!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.53,0:15:38.26,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why would Lisa Lisa have this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.79,0:15:41.92,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who are these people?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.96,0:15:45.79,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,May 1889?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.16,0:15:47.68,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's 50 years old!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.28,0:15:51.22,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This young man is Speedwagon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.29,0:15:53.47,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Granny Erina!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.84,0:15:57.56,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And Straizo is holding a baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.46,0:16:04.52,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lisa Lisa... I know nothing about\Nher life or her past.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.90,0:16:07.32,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why does she have these photos?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.74,0:16:53.51,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.76,0:16:55.49,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We accept your bargain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.40,0:16:58.66,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We'll fight you one-on-one!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.51,0:17:21.10,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You saw the photos.\NThat means you want to talk, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.60,0:17:24.81,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I had planned to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.14,0:17:26.44,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.90,0:17:30.19,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Fifty years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.03,0:17:36.45,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Erina lost her husband, Jonathan Joestar\Non a ship on the Atlantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.53,0:17:38.24,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He was your grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.20,0:17:43.45,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That day, your grandmother\Nsaved a baby girl's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.00,0:17:45.50,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.87,0:17:48.21,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The baby in that picture is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.00,0:17:50.71,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hang on now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.05,0:17:52.46,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That was 50 years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.76,0:17:55.70,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you were a baby 50 years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.70,0:17:59.27,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! How old are you, anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.14,0:18:02.35,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're 50?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.31,0:18:08.10,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I-If you're 50, that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.44,0:18:09.98,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,...y-you're old!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.28,0:18:15.31,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Right? Normally...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.82,0:18:18.99,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You look like you're in your late 20s.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.49,0:18:23.91,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They say Hamon energy is life energy\Nand keeps you young.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.50,0:18:29.75,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess you don't behave\Nlike a young woman should at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.04,0:18:33.02,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I think I see a wrinkle\Nbehind those shades!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.55,0:18:36.05,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.01,0:18:40.76,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now, prepare the arena!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.76,0:18:41.60,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Light the fires!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.65,0:18:53.32,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's no time to talk now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.15,0:18:56.07,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But we do need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.62,0:18:59.95,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My roots are connected to yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.95,0:19:00.95,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Our roots?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.66,0:19:04.37,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The mask killed my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.12,0:19:10.75,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Since Erina was pregnant\Nwhen she rescued me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.27,0:19:13.21,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,...I was raised by Straizo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.27,0:19:16.83,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you serious? By Straizo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.22,0:19:20.25,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Straizo taught me about Hamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.57,0:19:24.56,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Straizo gave me the Red Stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.88,0:19:29.06,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So S-Straizo is your foster father!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.89,0:19:35.43,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It is tragic that the fear of aging\Ndrove him to such madness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.02,0:19:41.16,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My feelings about you defeating him\Nare complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.90,0:19:44.03,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I feel it was destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.04,0:19:48.66,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What can I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.04,0:19:52.46,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I-It is very complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.38,0:19:55.84,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What a bizarre relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.42,0:20:01.18,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lisa Lisa carries\Na past full of sadness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.93,0:20:04.47,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo, we're out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.47,0:20:06.43,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's the rumbling?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.32,0:20:20.32,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They're here. Now the battle can begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.24,0:20:25.32,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,T-They're...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.83,0:20:35.88,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Out of the way!\NI don't care if you get crushed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.09,0:20:38.80,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is that a d-dinosaur?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.80,0:20:41.13,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, it's a horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.26,0:20:45.89,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Kars, Lord Wamuu, please move!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.89,0:20:48.23,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They've gone berserk!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.31,0:20:52.14,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Wamuu, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.86,0:21:02.32,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What fine steeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.28,0:21:09.79,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We used masks\Nto turn these horses into vampires.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.79,0:21:12.16,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,V-Vampire horses?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.12,0:21:20.30,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In this arena, JoJo will face Wamuu\Nin an ancient-style chariot duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.09,0:21:24.30,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A chariot duel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.63,0:21:27.35,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,An ancient Roman death match!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.35,0:21:31.43,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You'll ride through the arena\Nwhile you fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.64,0:21:38.81,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Wamuu or JoJo? Who will fall\Nor be beaten down while riding?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.81,0:21:40.63,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Defeat means death!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.63,0:21:42.28,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Those are the rules, JoJo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.44,0:21:44.70,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The beasts have 150 horsepower!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.85,0:21:47.91,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even Lord Wamuu can barely control them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.91,0:21:49.44,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.44,0:21:52.33,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fight you on any field!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.33,0:21:56.21,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But vampire horses\Nare your minions, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.62,0:22:00.63,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Worry not. The reins conduct Hamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.96,0:22:03.21,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wamuu will use his strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.46,0:22:06.77,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You can use Hamon to control them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.34,0:22:10.44,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is that right? They look vicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.87,0:22:12.35,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bite, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.81,0:22:20.48,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see. A little Hamon does it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.32,0:22:24.53,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wamuu! Wamuu! Wamuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.41,0:22:39.29,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wamuu chose an ancient form\Nfor this battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.29,0:22:41.42,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That means he's serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.59,0:22:47.09,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's not doing this for fun,\Nor making sport of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.80,0:22:51.52,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Beat him, JoJo. We have to win this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.00,0:22:53.06,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There are no draws!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.02,0:22:57.06,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wamuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.40,0:23:03.32,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't taken this antidote yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.57,0:23:07.74,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I promised Caesar I'd drink it\Nafter I kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.99,0:23:12.63,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That promise will give me\Npower I've never seen before!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.46,0:23:21.96,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Fight alongside me, Caesar!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.63,0:23:31.43,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I ride to battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.61,0:25:08.61,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.17,0:25:13.30,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wamuu! Wamuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.44,0:25:21.48,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Start!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.62,0:25:22.07,Type,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chapter 22: A True Warrior
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.07,0:25:24.07,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,
